headline.print_headline: Australian Ogilvy Doing the Barracuda in Style
headline.main: Australian Ogilvy Doing the Barracuda in Style

lead_paragraph: Geoff Ogilvy birdied the final hole to open a three-point lead after the third round at the $3 million Barracuda Championship in Reno, Nevada on Saturday.
